# LinkedIn Organic Content Strategy for B2B SaaS

## Objective

The purpose of this project is to research successful B2B SaaS content creators and identify patterns that drive organic growth on LinkedIn.

## Research Scope

This repository contains:

* Expert profiles
* LinkedIn post analysis
* Video research
* Key marketing insights
* Actionable content strategies

